{"tid":1080904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惡賊爬渠入屋笠頭毆劫，曉翠苑92歲獨居婦浴血","createTime":"2019-03-28T02:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T05:03:40.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7648f06e44f22d343e08dc2aa86f9114395c683","tid":1080904,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:18:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/967000-香港-【無良惡賊】爬渠入屋笠頭毆劫+曉翠苑92歲獨居婦浴血\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F967000-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E7%84%A1%E8%89%AF%E6%83%A1%E8%B3%8A%E3%80%91%E7%88%AC%E6%B8%A0%E5%85%A5%E5%B1%8B%E7%AC%A0%E9%A0%AD%E6%AF%86%E5%8A%AB%2B%E6%9B%89%E7%BF%A0%E8%8B%9192%E6%AD%B2%E7%8D%A8%E5%B1%85%E5%A9%A6%E6%B5%B4%E8%A1%80&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTl1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=e1e8a889\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F967000-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E7%84%A1%E8%89%AF%E6%83%A1%E8%B3%8A%E3%80%91%E7%88%AC%E6%B8%A0%E5%85%A5%E5%B1%8B%E7%AC%A0%E9%A0%AD%E6%AF%86%E5%8A%AB%2B%E6%9B%89%E7%BF%A0%E8%8B%9192%E6%AD%B2%E7%8D%A8%E5%B1%85%E5%A9%A6%E6%B5%B4%E8%A1%80&h=2a395040\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/967000-香港-【無良惡賊】爬渠入屋笠頭毆劫+曉翠苑92歲獨居婦浴血</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190328/_2019032808413597871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190328%2F_2019032808413597871.jpg&h=3ac0b175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">老婦面部受傷，清醒被送往東區醫院治理。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n柴灣曉翠苑碧翠閣3樓一名92歲獨居老婦，昨晚9時許懷疑遭賊人爬水渠攀廚房窗闖入行劫，期間遭賊人以被鋪蓋著頭部並撼向牆身，頭部受傷送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190328/_2019032807550373857.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190328%2F_2019032807550373857.jpg&h=b5a30dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">懷疑被打開的窗戶。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n老婦面部受傷，清醒被送往東區尤德夫人那打素醫院治理。據悉，賊人闖入時老婦已入睡，被吵醒後，賊人以被鋪將她蒙頭，老婦在反抗期間被毆傷，一度暈倒，直至凌晨甦醒後求助。而老婦育有3子1女，全已遷出，現時獨居。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190328/_2019032807560088775.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190328%2F_2019032807560088775.jpg&h=d579673d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警方到場調查。</span></div>"},{"pid":"e78acd136d05fbed2861914e506c02efe9363d5f","tid":1080904,"uid":68556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:19:49.000Z","msg":"依d仆街真係要揾出黎處決。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34e1d46f5d4f42aaf0a891205b900c5eb0d7b11","tid":1080904,"uid":181318,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"輸入內地人才計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a13243c0fa538b1534a9b6eda136c4779b21212","tid":1080904,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"印度人 ?"},{"pid":"8752cd4cd8873a86c1807d94ac1ab28146a797a0","tid":1080904,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f34e1d46f5d4f42aaf0a891205b900c5eb0d7b11","tid":1080904,"uid":181318,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T03:01:03.000Z","msg":"輸入內地人才計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8728e2c386c880428c082950e3f19733ad9566b6","tid":1080904,"uid":38982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T04:07:44